project_descr: Early recovery in Zamboanga after GPH-MNLF stand-off

outputs.output_descr: This project will strengthen the capacities of UNCO and UNDP to respond to the recovery needs of affected areas in the city of Zamboanga following the stand-off between military troops and factions within the MNLF in September/October 2013.

project_title: early recovery in zamboanga after gph-mnlf stand-off
